r las escritoras peruanas a finales de siglo. La antología de textos ensayísticos complementa el estudio y busca difundir los veintiséis textos primarios que constituyen el volumen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Spanish, Castilian.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aPeruvian literaturexWomen authors. 0aPeruvian prose literaturey19th century. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Caribbean & Latin American.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary Studies 2023z9783111318264oZDB-23-DSP40uhttps://doi.org/10.31819/978396869292040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783968692920423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783968692920/original  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2023  aZDB-23-DSPb2023